data.eml:eml: New Tortricidae (Lepidoptera) from East Africa with an account of the tortricid fauna of acacia in the Kenyan Rift Valley

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Agassiz, David J. L., Aarvik, Leif (2014): New Tortricidae (Lepidoptera) from East Africa with an account of the tortricid fauna of acacia in the Kenyan Rift Valley. Zootaxa 3861 (4): 369-397, DOI: http://dx.doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.3861.4.7
